    <Callout title="Location Tip" type="tip">
      Route 1 Bypass locations cost more but catch NH customers immediately upon crossing into Maine. If your budget allows, that visibility pays for itself in new customer acquisition. NH customers are making a deliberate trip — they will be looking for your sign. A prominent position on the Bypass ensures you capture that search intent before they potentially continue to other Maine dispensaries.
